Variable Documentation

KSZ8851SLN_mib_t mibCounters [static]

Copy of the current MIB counters values from the ksz8851snl.

This is updated by calling KSZ8851SNL_MIBCountersUpdate.

The datasheet recommends that the MIB counter values are read at least every 30 seconds because of counter overflow possibility.
